The United States strongly condemns the terrorist attack on the army recruitment center in Aden, Yemen. The attack has resulted in numerous deaths and injuries. The US offers condolences to the families of the victims and expresses concern about the political and security vacuum in Yemen that allows groups like al-Qaida and ISIL to exploit the situation. The US emphasizes the importance of stability in Yemen and urges the parties involved to cease fighting and work towards a lasting peace through the United Nations-facilitated process with support from the international community.